{"tid":1103431,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蒼井空4月30日晚剖腹產子　蒼老師全亞洲免費直播生B過程","createTime":"2019-04-12T11:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T04:39:09.000Z","uid":60207,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"05ec42082d5af4ec9a1a89576fce643ce6f1578b","tid":1103431,"uid":60207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"現年35歲的前AV女王蒼井空，去年嫁與DJ NON拉埋天窗，今年初蒼井空成功克服不孕，懷有雙胞胎，即將臨盆的蒼井空，早前宣布預產期為4月30日至5月1日期間，預備剖腹產子的蒼井空，更跟電視台合作直播BB出世一刻。<br />\n蒼井空雖然退出AV界，但人氣依然強勁，陀孖B的蒼老師，早前就宣布獲日本網上平台AbemaTV邀請，在4月30日晚上10時至5月1日下午5時預產當天作網上直播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2vGFRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2vGFRQ.jpg&h=3b5f4f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒼井空的生B直播名為「蒼井空出產當日亞洲同時直播～Welcome to the world, Sola&rsquo;s Baby」，更會在中國、台灣、韓國等地同時播出。蒼井空決定公開生B實況，她表示希望可以重要時刻留紀念，由平成直播到新時代令和，跟全亞洲的fans分享喜悅。<br />\n其實蒼井空在產前3個月，已接受製作單位貼身拍攝，蒼老師稱她雖非名流，就是讓人拍攝普通的生活，像我在家裡都沒化妝，一整天穿著睡衣，總之完全呈現現實生活的模樣」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8K4DDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8K4DDA.jpg&h=d35daa06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gMYUgqg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgMYUgqg.jpg&h=e0f91022&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒼井空懷有雙胞胎，不過她早前向傳媒坦言深感不安，因為非常擔心開刀麻醉藥藥效過後，怕忍受不了痛楚，以及害怕會留下傷痕。<br />\n不過當她經過同樣剖腹的好友所安慰下，心情已經平伏，早前還大方分享多款大肚寫集，被網友讚蒼老師充滿母愛。"},{"pid":"caacf48c496bf08b8e30331c40297560cc9f6272","tid":1103431,"uid":60207,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"俾人入就睇得多 有嘢出都係第一次睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23d4e1d130b01f3bb371283526db725fced42fc","tid":1103431,"uid":187544,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"唔係自然生，根本無野睇"},{"pid":"7284bd9afb83373796edbe560e196c6deedda710","tid":1103431,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"蒼老師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ecb2a56d8d4abec2a2cc8b3a93ef360aec90a1","tid":1103431,"uid":3063,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"caacf48c496bf08b8e30331c40297560cc9f6272","tid":1103431,"uid":60207,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"俾人入就睇得多 有嘢出都係第一次睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"個仔全亞洲男性都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fed665910af81bcf5e8ffd9b4adbd4e94fdd1814","tid":1103431,"uid":54431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"caacf48c496bf08b8e30331c40297560cc9f6272","tid":1103431,"uid":60207,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"俾人入就睇得多 有嘢出都係第一次睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:51:23.000Z","msg":"比人中出咪有精出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d832a6be6a8fa173984f92e911e788c9ab0ca031","tid":1103431,"uid":60207,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b4ecb2a56d8d4abec2a2cc8b3a93ef360aec90a1","tid":1103431,"uid":3063,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"caacf48c496bf08b8e30331c40297560cc9f6272","tid":1103431,"uid":60207,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"俾人入就睇得多 有嘢出都係第一次睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"個仔全亞洲男性都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:51